Many thanks to Miquel What the hell happened this weekend All I can say right now is thank you to everybody who showed up and made this weekend one of the most fun memories ever And thanks to Miguel and Blake again for organizing everything I couldnt have done it without yall Once I can put more full sentences together Ill write more Thanks again Bryan ps If anybody has seen my Carolina shirt my FW Many thanks to MiquelMessage From mailto Sent Monday June AM To otmailCom Espinosa sbStanfordEdu cwdNet ankunitedCom alpineCom Ed nronCom dqNet Warren otmailCom Bryan sfbCom Subject RE Many thanks to Miquel Excellent time Look forward to keeping it going at the wedding Elizabeth will be so impressed Speaking of keeping it going our good friend Mr Kimzey called me last night drunk as rodeo goat at about PM asking me to go out and party a little bit more Did I miss something or did we not get our share this weekend Apparently the weekend only caused Bryan to reflect on his current state of affairs By chance it was just the welts on his forehead from crushing cans that caused him to start boozing all by his lonesome yesterday Or perhaps he just wanted to enjoy the perks of first class Lets hope it was the latter and had nothing to do with the frightful prospect of being a married man in just weeks Oh by the way I can assure you all Kimzey has not read a single one of these emails yet and likely wont till about noon Damn slackers over there at CSFB Original Message From Clint Cobb mailto Sent Monday June AM To Nicholas JohnstonAdvisory otmailCom Espinosa sbStanfordEdu cwdNet Tennis SundayAfter church after lunchbrunch you are going down

SquashSorry I didnt get back to you We were on the go all weekend Two engagement parties for Susans brother and my th birthday on top of that Im available after work anytime this week besides tonight PSmy parents got me the same racket as you got for christmas It should be ready for domination this weekend
Tennis at My toe is feeling better How about tennis later this afternoon The we can have beers and watch the USA beat the cry baby Russians
